Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Inflation fears rise
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bv5p
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Oct 1978
Voters fear rising inflation as US business chiefs forecast recession. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.